              },
              "title": [
                {
                  "type": "Text",
                  "text": "Integration"
                }
              ],
              "children": [
                {
                  "kind": {
                    "type": "Paragraph",
                    "content": [
                      {
                        "type": "Text",
                        "text": "**Called by:**\n- **brainstorming** (Phase 4) - REQUIRED when design is approved and implementation follows\n- **subagent-driven-development** - REQUIRED before executing any tasks\n- **executing-plans** - REQUIRED before executing any tasks\n- Any skill needing isolated workspace\n\n**Pairs with:**\n- **finishing-a-development-branch** - REQUIRED for cleanup after work complete"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  "span": {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 0
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            "span": {
